This is the FIXED VERSION of surf_bigramp_v2.  If you are one of the 9 people who downloaded it in the 30minutes it was here, please upgrade.  


This map looks simple, but it sure isn't.

How it works is there's one main "Big Ramp" which goes the length of the map, and when you come to the end of the big ramp, you warp back to the top, going the direction you were going when you got to the end. So, as you do laps, you get faster and faster, until you are absolutely blazing.

Now, in the air above this main ramp are a series of high up small ramps, each leading to small portals thats take you to gun rooms, sniper spots, etc. When you come to the end of the big ramp and warp back up, you come out of the warp going the same direction and speed you were going before you warped! This means that if you flip up off the end of the "Big Ramp," you will come out the warp going up! This allows you to go higher and higher as you go faster and faster and learn to come out of the warp more skillfully, allowing you to turn and land on platforms or go up and land on ramps and platforms that at first appear inaccesible.

Of course there are also weapon rooms, hidden credits rooms,hidden shotgun platforms, pistol tunnels, warp rooms, glass tubes to land in, spike pits, billboards, invisible warps, "The Awp Box" , tiny ramps coming off the spine, platforms coming with hazard stairs, a human pinball machine, lots of surfing and secrets, and trick potential up the wazoo!

Enjoy! - Ø×²Surf ||Gai|| is PISSED!

__________________________________________
[Update] 4th of May 2007: Final version
Changes:
-Scaled down 0.75, to make rounds faster
-A couple of new textures
-Bugfixes
__________________________________________

Surf_Bathroom; Surf map to please everyone. Or atleast, that's what I was going for. 

Map Features:
-Rats-style, bathroom-themed map.
-Lighting
-3d Skybox
-Ramps fit in with the environment
-90% Custom textures
-Lots of surfing possibilities, with interesting boosters, double halfpipes etc. all looking natural.
-Functional tabs, hairdryers , sinks, breakables and a toilet that actually flushes.

Concept:
-Teams spawn seperately at opposite sides of the room.
-You get to pick one of 7 guns at spawn *new in v2*
-Snipers are available for pick-up all around the map, awp's are more challenging to get to then scouts.
-Going in any sink will tele you into a plumbing-system, spitting you out at a random location (Spawns, Bath, Shower, Sinks, Top, etc.)
-The Toilet becomes a bombzone after 2 minutes.
-No jail, you can safely surf down on the floor, but it can also kill you
-You can safely land on any towel
-There is a place called top, from where you can go just about everywhere using boosters.
-Secrets

This map is all about exploring and fighting; feel free. Do whatever you want. Choose to buy a gun and rush into the enmy, or go eco and surf for a sniper. Have fun surfing around, try stuff, try getting to places in different ways, fuck around on the boosters, or mess with the double halfpipe-cabinet. Both the beginners and skilled surfers can enjoy this.

I put way too many time in this, so you better like it, damnit.
**Changes in V2**
-Changed spawn, no more ubyzone, you get to pick a weapon.
-Removed some stuff
-Fixed not being able to pick up snipers on some servers
-Did a little bit of optimization

-SmOoth

This would be my first surf style map made simply because my clanmate told me to. Personally I felt the map is relatively easy to complete, but upon putting it on our server (8.3.6.35:27015), people were struggling to a degree. The lighting on the map is interesting and my warp tubes are pretty crazy. A helpful hint about the first tunnels: I find that if you get in there with some speed, simply holding W works to get you through. Another thing to note is that after you are shot upwards, make sure you turn around completely for that is where the map continues; that way and to the left in a bit. Enjoy the map!
